Programs:
~~~~~~~~
  charTest.e    - demo how to make a multi-dim array of characters.
  intTest.e     - demo how to make a multi-dim array of integers.
  longTest.e    - demo how to make a multi-dim array of long integers.

  longTest-1d.e - yes, you can even do one-dim arrays!
  4dtest.e      - test of the offset calculations for a four-dim array.

  charTesti.e   - for those who don't have EPP, here is a finished product,
                  ready to compile.
